# Review Summary Engine (Project-wise)

Step 0: repo + CSV inspection (no OpenAI calls)
Step 1: project-wise AI summaries using OpenAI API (structured output)
Step 2: per-review tag generation (3 tags per review)

Input CSV goes in: data/in/
Outputs go in: data/out/
